parameters: \TA[1]Thank you for coming even though I called you suddenly.
\TA[1]Ah, please give me one couple parfait!

\TA[1]But it's surprising. I thought it was about the notebook,
but it's actually a livestream.
\TA[1]Are you aiming for a tuba player?

\TA[1]Huh!? N-No, it's not like that. It's just a little hobby,
you know...

\TA[1]Well, recently there has been a significant increase in
people watching YouTube.

\TA[1]Did you download the app? Please lend me your smartphone so
I can set it up.

\TA[1]I've set up the basic settings, so if you just press this
button, the livestream should start right away.
\TA[1]Oh, I did it. It's really showing.

\TA[1]Senpai, you're using a smartphone with a pretty high-
performance camera, aren't you? It seems like it would be
good to shoot with a smartphone too, right?

\TA[1](I've never actually used it before because I don't have
anyone to take pictures with...)
$gameSystem.addLog("\\C[0]また新しい配信が始まったな");

\TA[1]There is a place where only new streamers are displayed. At
least 10 people will come in.
$gameSystem.addLog("\\C[0]配信してる方、もしかして女性ですか？");

\TA[1]There are all kinds of people on the internet, after all.
\TA[1]Anyway, this is roughly how it is. Did it help?
\TA[1]Yes, thanks to you, I was saved.
\TA[1]By the way, could you also show me your notebook?
